 === Guichan ===


This Folder is here to store Guichan release.
Guichan website is at http://guichan.sourceforge.net/

1) Get guichan at http://guichan.googlecode.com/files/guichan-0.8.2.tar.gz

2) unzip it in this folder

3) Make sure you have the folders in the right place
guichan/
	src
	include

4) remove the defaults front end folders ( allegro, hge, openlayer, opengl and sdl ) in src and include,
 as well as in src/contrib and include/contrib.

5) run CMake

6) Build Guichan with you usual compiler.

7) Use the built guichan library to built SDLut FE.
